      <title>小报首席执行官表示他压制了有关特朗普事务的负面报道</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/tabloid-ceo-says-he-squashed-negative-stories-on-trump-affairs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《国家问询报》所属公司的前负责人向纽约陪审团讲述了 2015 年的一次会议，当时他实际上成为了密谋者，密谋通过压制有关唐纳德·特朗普沉迷女色的负面报道来推动唐纳德·特朗普的总统竞选活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/tabloid-ceo-says-he-squashed-negative-stories-on-trump-affairs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 17:16:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩尔多瓦警告俄罗斯准备干涉西方政治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/russian-poised-for-political-meddling-in-the-west-moldova-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯正在采取多种措施——从人工智能生成的深度赝品到一袋袋现金——欧洲小国外交部长周五表示，摩尔多瓦的目的是破坏摩尔多瓦的民主，这是西方所期望的结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/russian-poised-for-political-meddling-in-the-west-moldova-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 17:10:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢拉欢迎委内瑞拉反对马杜罗的联合反对派</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/lula-welcomes-united-opposition-in-venezuela-election-against-maduro</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦对委内瑞拉反对派联合支持单一候选人的决定表示欢迎，称这将为尼古拉斯·马杜罗领导的陷入困境的国家举行潜在的合法选举奠定基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/lula-welcomes-united-opposition-in-venezuela-election-against-maduro</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 16:00:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官称争论“愚蠢”，特朗普可能会输掉禁言令之争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/trump-may-lose-contempt-fight-as-judge-calls-arguments-silly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普可能会因其社交媒体帖子而被判藐视法庭，这些帖子可能违反禁言令，因为负责监督他的封口费案的纽约法官将这位前总统律师的论点描述为“愚蠢”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/trump-may-lose-contempt-fight-as-judge-calls-arguments-silly</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 15:36:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大机构表示，Bunge 收购 Viterra 的交易引发了竞争危险信号</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/bunge-deal-for-viterra-raises-competition-red-flags-canadian-agency-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大反垄断监管机构对 Bunge Ltd. 拟议收购 Viterra Inc. 表示担忧，称这将对该国农业市场产生“重大反竞争影响”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/bunge-deal-for-viterra-raises-competition-red-flags-canadian-agency-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 15:31:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平在北约大使馆爆炸周年纪念日前往贝尔格莱德</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/xi-heads-to-belgrade-around-nato-embassy-bombing-anniversary</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预计习近平主席将在美国轰炸贝尔格莱德中国大使馆25周年前后访问贝尔格莱德，重点关注这一引发国内反美抗议并助长北京对北约不信任的事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/xi-heads-to-belgrade-around-nato-embassy-bombing-anniversary</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 15:20:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西门子首席执行官支持放宽德国投资债务规则的呼吁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/siemens-ceo-backs-calls-to-ease-german-debt-rules-for-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西门子首席执行官罗兰·布施 (Roland Busch) 也呼吁德国放宽借贷限制，以帮助为欧洲最大经济体的转型投资提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/siemens-ceo-backs-calls-to-ease-german-debt-rules-for-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 14:39:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟根据外国补贴法突袭安全设备公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/eu-raids-security-equipment-firm-under-foreign-subsidy-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟监管机构突袭了一家身份不明的安全设备公司的办公场所，这是对一项新法律的另一项测试，该法律旨在防止外国国家资助的公司滥用其财务实力来抵御欧盟竞争对手。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/eu-raids-security-equipment-firm-under-foreign-subsidy-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 14:24:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克承诺英国到 2030 年将 GDP 的 2.5% 用于军事</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/sunak-commits-uk-to-spending-2-5-of-gdp-on-military-by-2030</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 承诺到本十年末将国防开支增加到 GDP 的 2.5%，以缓解国内外对英国武装部队投资水平的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/sunak-commits-uk-to-spending-2-5-of-gdp-on-military-by-2030</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 13:50:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>石油市场认为伊朗制裁对出口影响不大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/oil-market-sees-iran-sanctions-having-muted-impact-on-exports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[推动乔·拜登加大对伊朗原油制裁力度的立法最早有望于本周成为法律。但不要指望总统会很快充分利用他的新权力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/oil-market-sees-iran-sanctions-having-muted-impact-on-exports</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 23:15:17 GMT</pubDate>
